data.description: Possible 4th bedroom in basement! Welcome to this gorgeous brick and stucco Bloom Carroll home with amazing 3 Seasons Room!  All big ticket items have been done for you-new furnace/air in 2018, all new windows 2018, new patio and deck 2018, new well pressure tank and hot water tank 2018 and new roof in 2014!  Gorgeous kitchen with hardwood flooring, granite countertops, massive island with pendant lighting and newer appliances.  Solid wood 6 panel doors. First Floor laundry.  Updated bathrooms.  Finished basement w/full egress window. New Azek tiered deck w/porclain tile on lower section.  3rd car garage is under 3 Seasons Room.  Private backyard!
